{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-19",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_19_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "The Russian's Hand",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 5,
  "page_total": 10,
  "page_start_sec": 994.656,
  "page_end_sec": 1235.6,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.559,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 994.656,
      "end": 996.18,
      "text": "Spade tossed it into Gutman's lap,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 996.3,
      "end": 996.48,
      "text": "saying,"
    },
    {
      "start": 997.3,
      "end": 999.12,
      "text": "Sit on it if you're afraid of losing it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1000.06,
      "end": 1001.18,
      "text": "You misunderstand me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1001.32,
      "end": 1002.94,
      "text": "Gutman replied suavely."
    },
    {
      "start": 1003.584,
      "end": 1004.96,
      "text": "It's not bad at all,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1005.04,
      "end": 1008.06,
      "text": "but business should be transacted in a business-like manner."
    },
    {
      "start": 1008.47,
      "end": 1010.32,
      "text": "He opened the flap of the envelope,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1010.52,
      "end": 1012.16,
      "text": "took out the thousand-dollar bills,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1012.64,
      "end": 1013.04,
      "text": "counted them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1013.08,
      "end": 1015.1,
      "text": "and chuckled so that his belly bounced."
    },
    {
      "start": 1015.9,
      "end": 1016.3,
      "text": "For instance,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1016.92,
      "end": 1018.7,
      "text": "there are only nine bills here now.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1019.6,
      "end": 1021.76,
      "text": "He spread them out on his fat knees and thighs.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1022.6,
      "end": 1024.3,
      "text": "There were ten when I handed it to you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1024.32,
      "end": 1025.38,
      "text": "as you very well know."
    },
    {
      "start": 1025.7,
      "end": 1028.66,
      "text": "His smile was broad and jovial and triumphant."
    },
    {
      "start": 1029.568,
      "end": 1031.64,
      "text": "Spade looked at Bridget O'Shaughnessy and asked,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1032.16,
      "end": 1032.36,
      "text": "Well?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1033.46,
      "end": 1035.36,
      "text": "She shook her head sidewise with emphasis.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1035.96,
      "end": 1037.2,
      "text": "She did not say anything,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1037.4,
      "end": 1038.88,
      "text": "though her lips moved slightly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1039.1,
      "end": 1040.62,
      "text": "as if she had tried to."
    },
    {
      "start": 1041.52,
      "end": 1042.54,
      "text": "Her face was frightened.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1043.68,
      "end": 1045.44,
      "text": "Spade held his hand out to Gutman and",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1045.44,
      "end": 1047.06,
      "text": "the fat man put the money into it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1047.712,
      "end": 1048.7,
      "text": "Spade counted the money,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1048.88,
      "end": 1051.06,
      "text": "nine thousand dollar bills,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1051.22,
      "end": 1052.56,
      "text": "and returned it to Gutman."
    },
    {
      "start": 1052.92,
      "end": 1056.1,
      "text": "Then Spade stood up and his face was dull and placid."
    },
    {
      "start": 1056.62,
      "end": 1058.78,
      "text": "He picked up the three pistols on the table."
    },
    {
      "start": 1059.14,
      "end": 1060.9,
      "text": "He spoke in a matter-of-fact voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 1061.52,
      "end": 1063.0,
      "text": "I want to know about this.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1063.82,
      "end": 1064.04,
      "text": "We,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1064.22,
      "end": 1065.92,
      "text": "he nodded at the girl,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1065.96,
      "end": 1067.12,
      "text": "but without looking at her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1067.24,
      "end": 1068.84,
      "text": "are going in the bathroom."
    },
    {
      "start": 1070.1,
      "end": 1072.4,
      "text": "The door will be open and I'll be facing it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1073.152,
      "end": 1074.86,
      "text": "Unless you want a three-story drop,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1075.04,
      "end": 1077.98,
      "text": "there's no way out of here except past the bathroom door."
    },
    {
      "start": 1078.944,
      "end": 1079.86,
      "text": "Don't try to make it.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1080.02,
      "end": 1080.12,
      "text": "Really,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1081.48,
      "end": 1081.76,
      "text": "sir,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1081.98,
      "end": 1083.06,
      "text": "Gutman protested,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1083.08,
      "end": 1084.28,
      "text": "it's not necessary,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1084.88,
      "end": 1087.24,
      "text": "and certainly not very courteous of you to",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1087.3,
      "end": 1088.4,
      "text": "threaten us in this manner."
    },
    {
      "start": 1089.42,
      "end": 1092.34,
      "text": "You must know that we've not the least desire to leave.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1093.536,
      "end": 1095.22,
      "text": "I'll know a lot when I'm through,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1095.42,
      "end": 1097.1,
      "text": "Spade was patient but resolute."
    },
    {
      "start": 1097.88,
      "end": 1098.94,
      "text": "This trick upsets things.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1099.64,
      "end": 1100.78,
      "text": "I've got to find the answer.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1101.36,
      "end": 1102.36,
      "text": "It won't take long.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1102.68,
      "end": 1104.4,
      "text": "He touched the girl's elbow."
    },
    {
      "start": 1104.66,
      "end": 1105.42,
      "text": "Come on."
    },
    {
      "start": 1105.89,
      "end": 1107.1,
      "text": "In the bathroom,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1107.26,
      "end": 1108.76,
      "text": "Bridget O'Shaughnessy found words."
    },
    {
      "start": 1109.48,
      "end": 1111.42,
      "text": "She put her hands up flat on Spade's chest",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1111.42,
      "end": 1113.73,
      "text": "and her face up close to his and whispered,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1113.76,
      "end": 1115.42,
      "text": "I did not take that bill,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1115.56,
      "end": 1115.78,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 1116.9,
      "end": 1117.72,
      "text": "I don't think you did,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1117.88,
      "end": 1118.28,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1118.4,
      "end": 1119.54,
      "text": "but I've got to know."
    },
    {
      "start": 1120.44,
      "end": 1121.36,
      "text": "Take your clothes off.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1122.4,
      "end": 1123.78,
      "text": "You won't take my word for it?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1124.4,
      "end": 1124.9,
      "text": "No,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1125.36,
      "end": 1125.66,
      "text": "take your"
    },
    {
      "start": 1125.72,
      "end": 1126.24,
      "text": "clothes off."
    },
    {
      "start": 1127.232,
      "end": 1128.04,
      "text": "I won't.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1128.72,
      "end": 1129.06,
      "text": "All right,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1129.24,
      "end": 1132.18,
      "text": "we'll go back to the other room and I'll have them taken off."
    },
    {
      "start": 1132.93,
      "end": 1134.96,
      "text": "she stepped back with a hand to her",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1134.96,
      "end": 1137.46,
      "text": "mouth her eyes were round and horrified"
    },
    {
      "start": 1138.24,
      "end": 1139.74,
      "text": "you would she asked",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1139.74,
      "end": 1143.84,
      "text": "through her fingers i will he said i've got to"
    },
    {
      "start": 1143.84,
      "end": 1145.9,
      "text": "know what happened to that bill and i'm not going"
    },
    {
      "start": 1145.9,
      "end": 1148.46,
      "text": "to be held up by anybody's maidenly modesty"
    },
    {
      "start": 1149.58,
      "end": 1149.68,
      "text": "oh",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1150.3,
      "end": 1153.4,
      "text": "it isn't that she came close to him and put her",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1153.4,
      "end": 1156.32,
      "text": "hands on his chest again i'm not ashamed to be"
    },
    {
      "start": 1156.32,
      "end": 1160.06,
      "text": "naked before you but can't you see not like this"
    },
    {
      "start": 1160.67,
      "end": 1162.5,
      "text": "Can't you see that if you make me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1162.64,
      "end": 1164.62,
      "text": "you'll be killing something?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1165.36,
      "end": 1167.16,
      "text": "He did not raise his voice.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1167.64,
      "end": 1169.54,
      "text": "I don't know anything about that."
    },
    {
      "start": 1170.2,
      "end": 1171.72,
      "text": "I've got to know what happened to the bill.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1172.22,
      "end": 1172.8,
      "text": "Take them off."
    },
    {
      "start": 1173.96,
      "end": 1175.34,
      "text": "She looked at his unblinking,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1175.52,
      "end": 1176.6,
      "text": "yellow-gray eyes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1176.88,
      "end": 1179.04,
      "text": "and her face became pink and then white again."
    },
    {
      "start": 1180.04,
      "end": 1182.58,
      "text": "She drew herself up tall and began to undress.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1183.18,
      "end": 1186.42,
      "text": "He sat on the side of the bathtub watching her and the open door.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1187.24,
      "end": 1188.68,
      "text": "No sound came from the living room.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1188.98,
      "end": 1191.54,
      "text": "She removed her clothes swiftly without fumbling,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1191.72,
      "end": 1193.7,
      "text": "letting them fall down on the floor around her"
    },
    {
      "start": 1193.7,
      "end": 1193.96,
      "text": "feet."
    },
    {
      "start": 1194.88,
      "end": 1195.68,
      "text": "When she was naked,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1195.78,
      "end": 1198.36,
      "text": "she stepped back from her clothing and stood looking at him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1199.46,
      "end": 1202.58,
      "text": "In her ming was pride without defiance or embarrassment.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1203.25,
      "end": 1204.56,
      "text": "He put his pistols on the",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1204.62,
      "end": 1205.46,
      "text": "toilet seat and,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1205.5,
      "end": 1206.18,
      "text": "facing the door,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1206.28,
      "end": 1208.26,
      "text": "went down on one knee in front of her garments."
    },
    {
      "start": 1209.12,
      "end": 1209.62,
      "text": "He picked up",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1209.66,
      "end": 1212.66,
      "text": "each piece and examined it with fingers as well as eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 1212.9,
      "end": 1215.1,
      "text": "He did not find the thousand-dollar bill."
    },
    {
      "start": 1215.69,
      "end": 1216.66,
      "text": "When he had finished,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1216.72,
      "end": 1217.32,
      "text": "he stood up,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1217.34,
      "end": 1219.06,
      "text": "holding her clothes out in his hands to her."
    },
    {
      "start": 1219.6,
      "end": 1219.78,
      "text": "Thanks,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1220.04,
      "end": 1220.54,
      "text": "he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 1220.72,
      "end": 1221.68,
      "text": "Now I know."
    },
    {
      "start": 1222.82,
      "end": 1224.1,
      "text": "She took the clothing from him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1224.24,
      "end": 1225.58,
      "text": "She did not say anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 1226.2,
      "end": 1227.52,
      "text": "He picked up his pistols.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1228.0,
      "end": 1230.84,
      "text": "He shut the bathroom door behind him and went into the living room."
    },
    {
      "start": 1231.808,
      "end": 1234.38,
      "text": "Gutman smiled amiably at him from the rocking chair.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1235.296,
      "end": 1235.6,
      "text": "Find it?",
      "para_break": true
    }
  ]
}